body:
The list of supported ops are available [here](https://github.com/tensorflow/tensorflow/blob/master/tensorflow/contrib/lite/g3doc/tf_ops_compatibility.md). The two recommended solutions are:
1. Add a custom op as described [here](https://github.com/tensorflow/tensorflow/blob/master/tensorflow/contrib/lite/g3doc/custom_operators.md).
2. Only use the ops that are currently supported by TFLite in your model.
